name: $rest-hook
desc: The channel is executed by sending a packet across a web socket connection maintained by the client. The URL identifies the websocket, and the client binds to this URL.

name: $websocket
desc: The channel is executed by sending an email to the email addressed in the URI (which must be a mailto:).

name: $email
desc: The channel is executed by sending an SMS message to the phone number identified in the URL (tel:).

name: $sms
desc: The channel is executed by sending a message (e.g. a Bundle with a MessageHeader resource etc.) to the application identified in the URI.
